| Field                                            | Type          | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
+--------------------------------------------------+---------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| decode(encode('testtest','password'),'password') | varbinary(32) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
+--------------------------------------------------+---------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
drop table test;

